SSH Agent Forwarding
*****************************

cd ~/.ssh
nano confog

Host <IP/domain>
  ForwardAgent yes


# Usually not needed on linux
* Your ssh-agent must be running before you ssh into server: try -- eval `ssh-agent`
* Your valid Id must be on use by ssh-agent before you ssh into server : try -- ssh-add ~/.ssh/your_key
* Make sure other ssh config are not overriding our config and ~/.ssh/config is being loaded -- ssh -v URL
